## Pattern

```gherkin
@Rule(NN)
Rule: [Rule name]

  @Scenario(NN)
  Scenario: [Testable behavior]
    Given [precondition]
    When [action]
    Then [observable outcome]
```

## Verify

```bash
namako gate --specs-dir test/specs
```

**Note:** This creates binding work — adding scenarios with new steps will require bindings in a follow-up mission.
